<div class="card card-body bg-light">
	<button type="button" class="btn btn-info btn-sm fs-5 fw-bold">
		Isaiah 9:6-7
	</button>
	<blockquote class="blockquote">
		<sup class="fw-bold text-primary">6</sup> For a child will be born to us, a son will be given to us;
		And the government will rest on His shoulders;
		And His name will be called Wonderful Counselor, Mighty God,
		Eternal Father, Prince of Peace.<br />
		<sup class="fw-bold text-primary">7</sup> There will be no end to the increase of His government or of peace,
		On the throne of David and over his kingdom,
		To establish it and to uphold it with justice and righteousness
		From then on and forevermore.
		The zeal of the Lord of hosts will accomplish this.
	</blockquote>
</div>

